    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi!</p>

<p>I was wondering if there is any way to link select fields together?
So that if "value1" is selected in element 1, element 2 displays only the values corresponding to "value1" of the first field.</p>

<p>For example:
- Select 1: Country
- Select 2: State
- If Country "US" is selected, the right states are displayed...</p>

<p>I think this could be done with some query/filter options in the FilteringSelect-Datastore or something like this?</p>

<p>A direct integration into the framework would be great in one of the next major versions is possible...</p>

<p>Greets, Mat.</p>

